trans-unit.source: Provides the content for a high fidelity, fixed-format page.
trans-unit.target: Fornece o conteúdo para uma alta-fidelidade, página formato fixo.

trans-unit.source: FixedPage is typically used to provide the content for a page within a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument>.
trans-unit.target: FixedPage é normalmente utilizado para fornecer o conteúdo para uma página dentro de um <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument>.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument>

trans-unit.source: FixedPage automatically defines page breaks at the start and end of its content.
trans-unit.target: FixedPage define automaticamente as quebras de página no início e no fim do respetivo conteúdo.

trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a rectangle defining the overflow area for bleeds, registration marks, and crop marks.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define um retângulo de definir a área de capacidade excedida para as marcas de cortar, bleeds e marcas de registo.

trans-unit.source: BleedBox is used to specify an expanded area for print production-related bleeds, registration marks, and crop marks that may extend outside the logical page.
trans-unit.target: BleedBox é utilizada para especificar uma área expandida para impressão bleeds relacionadas com a produção, as marcas de registo e marcas de cortar poderão estender fora da página lógica.

trans-unit.source: The logical page is the part of the sheet that will remain after it has been cropped to its final size.
trans-unit.target: A página lógica é a parte da folha de irá permanecer após ter sido recortada ao seu tamanho final.

trans-unit.source: So the dimensions of the bleed box can be no smaller than the logical page size, but may be greater.
trans-unit.target: As dimensões da caixa de bleed podem não pode ser inferior ao tamanho lógico de página, mas podem ser maiores.

trans-unit.source: Contrast the BleedBox with the <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage.ContentBox%2A> which is the area of the page on which content can appear; that is, the part of the page that is *within* the margins.
trans-unit.target: Contraste BleedBox com o <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage.ContentBox%2A>que é a área da página na qual pode aparecer conteúdo; ou seja, a parte da página que é *dentro* as margens.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage.ContentBox%2A>

trans-unit.source: So the dimensions of the content box can be no larger than the page, but may be smaller.
trans-unit.target: As dimensões da caixa de conteúdo podem não ser que a página, mas podem ser mais pequenas.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Rect.Left%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Rect.Right%2A> properties of both the bleed box and the content box are measured from the left and the <xref:System.Windows.Rect.Top%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Rect.Bottom%2A> properties are measured from the top.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Windows.Rect.Left%2A>e <xref:System.Windows.Rect.Right%2A>as propriedades da caixa de bleed e a caixa de conteúdo são avaliadas da esquerda e <xref:System.Windows.Rect.Top%2A>e <xref:System.Windows.Rect.Bottom%2A>propriedades são avaliadas da parte superior.</xref:System.Windows.Rect.Bottom%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Rect.Top%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Rect.Right%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Rect.Left%2A>

trans-unit.source: Hence, the following rules must be enforced in defining the BleedBox and <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage.ContentBox%2A>: - BleedBox.<xref:System.Windows.Rect.Left%2A> must be less than or equal to <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage.ContentBox%2A>.<xref:System.Windows.Rect.Left%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Por conseguinte, as seguintes regras devem ser forçadas em definir a BleedBox e <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage.ContentBox%2A>:-BleedBox.<xref:System.Windows.Rect.Left%2A> tem de ser menor ou igual a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage.ContentBox%2A>.<xref:System.Windows.Rect.Left%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Rect.Left%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage.ContentBox%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Rect.Left%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage.ContentBox%2A>

trans-unit.source: - BleedBox.<xref:System.Windows.Rect.Top%2A> must be less than or equal to <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage.ContentBox%2A>.<xref:System.Windows.Rect.Top%2A>.
trans-unit.target: -BleedBox. <xref:System.Windows.Rect.Top%2A>tem de ser menor ou igual a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage.ContentBox%2A>.<xref:System.Windows.Rect.Top%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Rect.Top%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage.ContentBox%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Rect.Top%2A>

trans-unit.source: - BleedBox.<xref:System.Windows.Rect.Right%2A> must be greater than or equal to <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage.ContentBox%2A>.<xref:System.Windows.Rect.Right%2A>.
trans-unit.target: -BleedBox. <xref:System.Windows.Rect.Right%2A>tem de ser maior que ou igual a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage.ContentBox%2A>.<xref:System.Windows.Rect.Right%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Rect.Right%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage.ContentBox%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Rect.Right%2A>

trans-unit.source: - BleedBox.<xref:System.Windows.Rect.Bottom%2A> must be greater than or equal to <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage.ContentBox%2A>.<xref:System.Windows.Rect.Bottom%2A>.
trans-unit.target: -BleedBox. <xref:System.Windows.Rect.Bottom%2A>tem de ser maior que ou igual a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage.ContentBox%2A>.<xref:System.Windows.Rect.Bottom%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Rect.Bottom%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedPage.ContentBox%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Rect.Bottom%2A>

trans-unit.source: The following rules must be enforced in defining the ContentBox: - ContentBox.<xref:System.Windows.Rect.Left%2A> must be greater than or equal to zero (0), and less than or equal to (ContentBox.<xref:System.Windows.Rect.Right%2A>-1).

trans-unit.source: - ContentBox.<xref:System.Windows.Rect.Top%2A> must be greater than or equal to zero (0), and less than or equal to (ContentBox.<xref:System.Windows.Rect.Bottom%2A>-1).
trans-unit.target: -ContentBox. <xref:System.Windows.Rect.Top%2A>tem de ser maior que ou igual a zero (0) e menor ou igual a (ContentBox.<xref:System.Windows.Rect.Bottom%2A> -1).</xref:System.Windows.Rect.Bottom%2A></xref:System.Windows.Rect.Top%2A>

trans-unit.source: - ContentBox.<xref:System.Windows.Rect.Right%2A> must be greater than or equal to (ContentBox.<xref:System.Windows.Rect.Left%2A>+1).
trans-unit.target: -ContentBox. <xref:System.Windows.Rect.Right%2A>tem de ser maior que ou igual a (ContentBox.<xref:System.Windows.Rect.Left%2A> +1).</xref:System.Windows.Rect.Left%2A></xref:System.Windows.Rect.Right%2A>

trans-unit.source: - ContentBox.<xref:System.Windows.Rect.Bottom%2A> must be greater than or equal to (ContentBox.<xref:System.Windows.Rect.Top%2A>+1).
trans-unit.target: -ContentBox. <xref:System.Windows.Rect.Bottom%2A>tem de ser maior que ou igual a (ContentBox.<xref:System.Windows.Rect.Top%2A> +1).</xref:System.Windows.Rect.Top%2A></xref:System.Windows.Rect.Bottom%2A>

trans-unit.source: The child element's bottom offset does not affect the size of the parent canvas.
trans-unit.target: O desvio de parte inferior do elemento subordinado não afeta o tamanho da tela principal.

trans-unit.source: If both a top and a bottom offset have been specified on the same element, the top offset takes precedence.
trans-unit.target: Se uma parte superior e um desvio inferior foram especificadas no mesmo elemento, o deslocamento superior tem precedência.

trans-unit.source: When setting the bottom offset as a percentage, the percentage value is based on the size of the parent canvas.

trans-unit.target: Se à esquerda e um deslocamento direito foram especificadas no mesmo elemento, o deslocamento esquerdo tem precedência.

trans-unit.source: When setting the right offset as a percentage, the percentage value is based on the width of the parent canvas.
trans-unit.target: Ao definir o deslocamento direito como uma percentagem, o valor de percentagem baseia-se na largura da tela principal.

trans-unit.source: The element on which to set the right offset.
trans-unit.target: O elemento no qual pretende definir o deslocamento direito.

trans-unit.source: The new distance between the right side of the element and the right side of its parent canvas.
trans-unit.target: A novo distância entre à direita do elemento e à direita da tela respetivo elemento principal.

trans-unit.source: Sets the distance between the top of an element and the top of its parent <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Canvas"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Define a distância entre a parte superior de um elemento e a parte superior do respetivo elemento principal <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Canvas"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The child element's top offset does not affect the size of the parent canvas.
trans-unit.target: Deslocamento superior do elemento subordinado não afeta o tamanho da tela principal.

trans-unit.source: If both a top and bottom offset have been specified on the same element, the top offset takes precedence.
trans-unit.target: Se um parte superior e inferior desvio foram especificado no mesmo elemento, o deslocamento superior tem precedência.

trans-unit.source: When setting the top offset as a percentage, the percentage value is based on the size of the parent canvas.
trans-unit.target: Ao definir a parte superior desvio como uma percentagem, o valor de percentagem baseia-se no tamanho da tela principal.

trans-unit.source: The element on which to set the top offset.
trans-unit.target: O elemento no qual pretende definir o deslocamento superior.

trans-unit.source: The new distance between the top side of the element and the top side of its parent canvas.
trans-unit.target: A novo distância entre o lado superior do elemento e no lado superior da tela respetivo elemento principal.
